headline: Alliant Energy (LNT) Q1 Earnings and Revenues Top Estimates
summary: Alliant Energy (LNT) delivered earnings and revenue surprises of 45.61% and 0.17%, respectively, for the quarter ended March 2025. Do the numbers hold clues to what lies ahead for the stock?

headline: Alliant Energy: Q1 Earnings Snapshot
summary: The Madison, Wisconsin-based company said it had profit of 83 cents per share. The results exceeded Wall Street expectations. The average estimate of three analysts surveyed by Zacks Investment Research was for earnings of 57 cents per share.
